ActFarm Credit Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of RUSSEL MARCOUX of Saskatoon, Saskatchewan, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Marilyn Marie Scott, whose term has expired.
